---
title: "US24 — Follow other users"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UserProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>FollowUser / UnfollowUser
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Follow
  A->>B: tap "Add Friend"
  B->>C: follow(targetId)
  C->>E: followUser(targetId)
  E-->>C: Follow (follower → followed)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (following)
  B-->>A: button now "Unfriend" - their posts join the feed
  A->>B: tap "Unfriend"
  B->>C: unfollow(targetId)
  C->>E: unfollowUser(targetId)
  E-->>C: removed
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (not following)
  B-->>A: button back to "Add Friend"
  note over E: followUser / unfollowUser via SocialGateway → follows (RLS) [planned]
